<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Ecodemy</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 0;
            text-align: center;
            border-top-left-radius: 8px;
            border-top-right-radius: 8px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .content h1 {
            color: #333333;
        }
        .content p {
            color: #666666;
        }
        .activation-code {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #4CAF50;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            padding: 10px 0;
            text-align: center;
            color: #999999;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #4CAF50;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Welcome to Ecodemy!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h1>Hello, <%= name %>!</h1>
            <p>Thank you for registering with Ecodemy. We're excited to have you on board!</p>
            <p>Please use the following activation code to activate your account:</p>
            <div class="activation-code"><%= activationCode %></div>
            <p>The code will expire in 5 min.</p>
            <p>If you have any questions, feel free to <a href="mailto:support@becodemy.com">contact us</a>.</p>
            <p>Best regards,<br>The Ecodemy Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2024 Ecodemy. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p><a href="https://www.Ecodemy.com">Visit our website</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
